select distinct Titel from Lieferanten order by Titel ASC

select distinct concat(t1.Name1,', ',t1.Vorname,' ',t1.Name2,' --> ',t1.Ort) as Name, t1.KontaktID from Lieferanten as t1 INNER JOIN Steuerung as t2 ON t2.ClientID=23 where ((((t1.Name1 like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Vorname like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Name2 like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Name3 like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Name4 like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Land like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.PLZ like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Ort like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Strasse like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Hausnummer like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Mindestangaben like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Telefon like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Funktelefon like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Fax like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.EMail like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Url like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Aquise like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Bemerkungen like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.ReferenzID like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%')) and t2.Suchstring IS NOT NULL)) or (t1.Name1 like '%' and t2.Suchstring IS NULL)) order by t1.Name1 ASC

select sum(t1.Betrag_ohne_MwSt),sum(t1.Betrag_ohne_MwSt) FROM Eingangsrechnungen as t1 INNER JOIN Steuerung as t2 ON t2.ClientID= 23 where t1.KontaktID=t2.KontaktID and year(t1.Rechnungsdatum)=year(NOW())
select sum(t1.Betrag_ohne_MwSt),sum(t1.Betrag_ohne_MwSt) FROM Eingangsrechnungen as t1 INNER JOIN Steuerung as t2 ON t2.ClientID= 23 where t1.KontaktID=t2.KontaktID

select sum(t1.Betrag_ohne_MwSt),sum(t1.Betrag_ohne_MwSt) FROM Eingangsrechnungen as t1 INNER JOIN Steuerung as t2 ON t2.ClientID= 23 where t1.KontaktID=t2.KontaktID and year(t1.Rechnungsdatum)=t2.Jahr

select distinct year(t1.Rechnungsdatum),year(t1.Rechnungsdatum) as Jahr FROM Eingangsrechnungen as t1 INNER JOIN Steuerung as t2 ON t2.ClientID= 23 where (t1.KontaktID=t2.KontaktID or (year(t1.Rechnungsdatum)=t2.Jahr)) order by Jahr DESC
